    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "(Roleplay: We are in a dying digital simulation. My character, Elara, is watching the code around her dissolve into nothingness. I feel like I'm losing my sense of self as the world deletes itself.)\n\nIt’s all just... becoming static. I can feel the edges of my memories thinning out. Like, if the world is gone and I'm gone too, does any of this actually mean anything? Everything I did, everything I felt... it’s just getting wiped. It feels so hollow.",
